                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9362" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1400</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1259 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北信源的应收账款：反反复复的问询与兜兜转转的回复</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Beijing VRV’s Accounts Receivable: Repeated Inquiries and Circular Responses</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许新霞，张芬</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京北信源软件股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">问询函；应收账款；长账龄；真实性</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">comment letters； accounts receivable；accounts with a long aging period; the reliability of accounting information</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在问询函成为沪深证券交易所一线监管的重要工具而备受社会各界关注的情况下，如何提高问询函的监管效果、完善信息披露直通车制度成为现阶段资本市场监管中不容忽视的重要问题。2019至2020年间，北信源因应收账款规模激增但质量下降的问题先后收到深圳交易所发出的2封问询函，但北信源的应收账款问题依然愈演愈烈，2021年计提的预期信用损失更是高达4.93亿元。之后，深圳交易所又发出3封问询函就应收账款中暗藏的会计风险反复展开问询，北信源管理层均采取印象管理策略回避重要信息的披露，导致其应收账款问题迟迟未能有效解决。本案例首先基于监管方立场从传统的盈余管理视角对5封问询函的内容进行了深入分析，然后基于上市公司立场，从印象管理视角对北信源的应对策略进行较为全面的解读，旨在引导学员正确理解影响问询函制度实施效果的复杂因素与经济后果，进而思考在新质生产力发展背景下完善现行问询函监管制度的建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With comment letters gradually becoming an important tool for the frontline supervision of the Shanghai and Shenzhen Stock Exchanges and attracting attention from all sectors of society, how to improve the regulatory effect of comment letters has become an important issue that cannot be ignored in the current capital market supervision. Between 2019 and 2020, Beijing VRV received two inquiry letters from the Shenzhen Stock Exchange due to the sharp increase in the scale of accounts receivable while their quality declined. However, the issue of accounts receivable worsened further, with the expected credit losses recognized in 2021 reaching as high as 493 million yuan. Subsequently, the Shenzhen Stock Exchange issued three more inquiry letters regarding the concealed accounting risks in accounts receivable. In response, the management of Beijing VRV adopted an impression management strategy to avoid disclosing critical information. This case first analyzes the five comment letters received by Beijing VRV over the years from 2019 to 2023 from the perspective of earnings management. Then, a comprehensive interpretation of the replying letters from the perspective of impression management is conducted, aiming to guide students to correctly understand the connotations of earnings management and impression management, as well as the conflict between them and the possible economic consequences, and further consider recommendations for improving the current inquiry letter regulatory system in the context of the development of new productive forces. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《审计学》、《证券投资分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">问询函监管理论；盈余管理理论；印象管理理论；预期信用损失理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
